injury.description: Aug 17: Browning (ribs) won't play in Saturday's preseason game against Chicago, Paul Dehner Jr. of The Athletic reports.
Aug 19: Head coach Zac Taylor told reporters Monday that Hubbard (knee) will go through individual work this week, Charlie Goldsmith of The Cincinnati Enquirer reports.
Aug 12: Mims is expected to be sidelined several weeks due to a strained pectoral muscle, Ben Baby of ESPN reports.
